text: Cosmin Atodiresei (born 1 March 1994) is a Romanian luger. He competed in the men's doubles event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male lugers Category:Olympic lugers of Romania Category:Lugers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
